Library has `(modes :standard)` so it also builds for bytecode / native

  $ dune build lib/.mylib.objs/byte/mylib.cmo
  $ dune build lib/.mylib.objs/native/mylib.cmx

Targets are promoted to the source tree

  $ ls ./dist
  hello.js
  lib
  node_modules
  $ ls ./dist/lib
  mylib.js

  $ node ./dist/hello.js
  hello

